    "There was a weak but significant association between students' confidence in academic writing and views on use of GAI technologies when other students use them for both grammar γ = 0.051, P < 0.05, N = 2522 and writing an entire essay γ = 0.130, P < 0.001, N = 2515 (Tables 7 and 8).",
